;   var_pim2 = mPIM * 1.285156  (scale by 329/256, converts to pressure units)
;   var_pim2 = 0 at atmospheric pressure (1 bar), increases with boost
;
; On out-of-range:
;   Uses default value 0x6666 for up to 15 consecutive errors.
;   After 15 errors: sets error flags (var_error_flags1.5, var_diag_errors_5.3)
;
; Also computes:
;   unk_144 = var_pim2 / 2 / 97 = pressure lookup table index for boost limit
;   var_nv_trim_unk_98: PIM calibration trim value stored in PRAM
